data.description: This charming Cape Cod style home with in ground pool offers you quality four season living space inside and out. The cozy eat in kitchen is equipped with new stainless steel appliances, large sink, a propane stove, subway tiles, and a quartz countertop. Four spacious bedrooms and two recently renovated bathrooms. The large laundry room with a wash station is perfect for pets. Recent updates within the last four years include central air mini splits, new furnace, new roof, new kitchen, new bathrooms, new electric, drywall, fresh paint, recently refinished hardwood flooring and vinyl flooring throughout. Large partially finished basement adds to the possibilities for this home. Outside enjoy the fully fenced yard, a large, maintenance-free Trex deck, and of course the heated inground saltwater pool for splashing around with friends all summer long.
